        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "By default, QuickShare keeps the access keys for your shared\n\t\t\t\tnotes in a hidden file in your vault. This enables updating or deleting of QuickShare notes from multiple\n\t\t\t\tdevices when using Obsidian Sync. If your vault folder is shared or public, it is recommended that you turn this setting off.",
          "target": "默认情况下，QuickShare 将您共享笔记的访问密钥保存在库中的一个隐藏文件中。这使得在使用 Obsidian Sync 时可以从多个设备更新或删除 QuickShare 笔记。如果您的库文件夹是共享或公开的，建议您关闭此设置。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Server URL hosting the encrypted notes. For more information about self-hosting, see https://github.com/mcndt/noteshare.space#deployment",
