        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Use the filename as the title of the note (like \"Show inline title\" in Obsidian's appearance settings). If unchecked, the title will be the first heading in the note.",
          "target": "使用文件名作为笔记标题（类似于 Obsidian 外观设置中的“显示内联标题”）。如果未勾选，标题将是笔记中的第一个标题。"
